			Spenden fÃ¼r Erinnerungen		</a>
		</h4>


	

<p><em>Autorin:Â Claudia Birkholz;</em><em>Â Fotos: Bundeswehr/ Birkholz / SternenbrÃ¼cke</em></p>
<p>Hamburg, 18.03.2019</p>
<div style="float: left; padding-right: 50px;"><a href="/images/Artikel/Spendenuebergabe/1.jpg" class="thumbnail zoomin" style="" rel="lightbox-mod_articles_news_content_5ca5bdcd06169" title=""></a>
