			Schwarzer Kontinent in Hamburg		</a>
		</h4>


	

<p>Â <em>Autor: Stefan Berger;</em><em> Fotografin: Lene Bartel<br /></em></p>
<p>Hamburg, 06.03.2019</p>
<div style="float: left; padding-right: 50px;"><a href="/images/Artikel/Ostafrika_2019/1.jpg" class="thumbnail zoomin" style="" rel="lightbox-mod_articles_news_content_5ca5bdcd116e7" title=""></a>
